item.title: about
item.description: About Me Hello! I’m Juan Yi, it’s pronounced Jew-Aren’t-E. People usually just call me Johnny. I’m a computer science and maths student at the University of Toronto. I’m actively dabbling in research and am hoping to explore the ever-hyped yet ever-interesting field of machine learning in the future. I’m using this website/blog to publish my thoughts on stuff I find interesting and anything that I think could be valuable for
